ARM: multi_v7_defconfig: Select CONFIG_MACH_BERLIN_BG2Q

Now that we support Berlin BG2Q, select CONFIG_MACH_BERLIN_BG2Q so that we can
boot BG2Q based boards like the BG2Q DMP.

